  21:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V5.12:<br>
  22:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 CIA402 3: change define "CIA402_DEVICE" to "CiA402_SAMPLE_APPLICATION"<br>
  23:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 CIA402 4: decouple CIA402 state machine and application from ESM (according ETG.6010, clause 
  24:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 COE4: update default entry name handling in case of 16Bit characters, add CoE Read/write indi
  25:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 ECAT 5: check inputsize before calling PDO_InputMappingdo not call PDO_InputMapping in case o
  26:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 ECAT 6: change input mapping trigger in case of DC Sync<br>
  27:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 ECAT1: handle Sync mapped to AL Event<br>
  28:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 ECAT4: set delay between EEPROM access retries to 10ms<br>
  29:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 EEPROM1: update eeprom reload in case of ESC 32Bit access (and the small eeprom emulation)<br
  30:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.13 TEST6: add 0xA002 monitoring ob function calls<br>
  31:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V5.11:<br>
  32:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 APPL1: add optional application function called from the main loop (after mbx and esm are exe
  33:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 BOOT1: add a bootloader sample application (only the ESM and FoE is supported)<br>
  34:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 COE4: add timestamp object (0x10F8) and update diagnosis handling<br>
  35:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 ECAT1: update SM Parameter measurement (based on the system time), enhancement for input only
  36:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 ECAT3: update PD monitoring variables even if the slave is not in OP, disable all interrupts 
  37:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 ECAT5: update Sync error counter/flag handling,check enum memory alignment depending on the p
  38:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 ECAT8: reset appl function pointer on startup, update timeout calculation during eeprom acces
  39:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 EEPROM1: get read size from register 0x502.6<br>
  40:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 EEPROM2: clear CRC Error bit only in case of a valid reload, write station alias only in case
  41:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.12 EEPROM3: implement a store EEPROM timeout handler<br>
  42:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V5.10.1:<br>
  43:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.11 COE3: change 0x10F3.2 (Sync Error limit) from UINT32 to UINT16 (according to the ETG.1020)<br
  44:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.11 ECAT1: update EEPROM access reset operation<br>
  45:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.11 ECAT10: change PROTO handling to prevent compiler errors<br>
  46:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.11 ECAT11: create application interface function pointer, add eeprom emulation interface functio
  47:../SSC/Src/ecatappl.c **** V5.11 ECAT2: update EEPROM access retry cycle (add 10ms delay between two retry cycles)<br>
